result.title: ByteCode 2016
result.content:
Hello Everyone!!

Bytecode 2016 is scheduled to be held on 26th February 2016, Friday from 20:30 Hrs IST to 01:30 Hrs IST. Prizes worth 1500 USD to be won !!!

If you are from a different time zone, you can check the corresponding start time here: http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=ByteCode+2016&iso=20160226T2030&p1=553

Registration for the contest is free and open to all. Participation can be in teams of at most 3 members.

To be eligible for prizes, register here at http://prgy.in/bytecode

Contest link: http://codechef.com/BYCO2016
